    "discriminators": [
     "A DOPPLER pass-by: the whole event is a monotonic downward spectral trajectory as the round closes and recedes. spectral_centroid_slope_hz_per_second is strongly NEGATIVE and the centroid modulates hard inside a very short window. That trajectory IS the subcategory.",
     "Against BULLETS-RICOCHET, the other sweeping subcategory: a by is NOISE that sweeps (harmonicity near zero — a fwip or a crack of air); a ricochet is a PITCH that sweeps (a whine with a measurable f0). Harmonicity is the split.",
     "Against BULLETS-IMPACT: a by never terminates in a hard transient — it is all air, no strike. Against SWOOSHES-SWISH: identical physics, much shorter and much brighter; only text names the bullet."
    ],
    "confusable_with": [
     "BLLTRico",
